title: VC joins national “in” campaign board ahead of EU referendum (The University of Liverpool)
text: ( Source : The University of Liverpool ) The national 'in' campaign, to be called Britain Stronger in Europe , announces its board today. Professor Janet Beer , Vice-Chancellor of the University of Liverpool and Vice-President of Universities UK
